title: FDL Fire/Rescue headed to barn fire
text:
FDL Fire/Rescue headed to barn fire Gannett Wisconsin Media 8:38 p.m. CDT October 20, 2015 Police report. 3 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Fond du Lac Fire/Rescue is responding to a request for mutual aid at barn fire in St. Cloud, according to a post on its Twitter account. 
There are several agencies responding to the blaze on Glen Road near Division Street, according to preliminary scanner information.
